node.text: Dope Amazon tingz. The Queen cleared her vocals. ✨#FeelingMyself

🩰 7 years later. Who remembers witnessing the internet break when I dropped this picture? ☺️😩 First solo female rap video to reach a billion views + first one to break the VEVO record for most views in a day chi… yes ma’am always inspiring the girlies 🥰#BarbTalk 🦄 #Anaconda #7YearAnniversary S/O Sir MixALot 💕 love you guys for holding me down this long 🎀 Pauz
